OL,3,CLib Dems call for 'like-minded' groups
OL,4,Cto work together post election
OL,6,FThe Liberal Democrats have become the
OL,7,Ffirst political group to publicly call
OL,8,Ffor cross-party cooperation to run
OL,9,FBirmingham City Council after
OL,10,Felections left the authority with no
OL,11,Foverall control.
OL,13,FFollowing his re-election as leader of
OL,14,Fthe Liberal Democrat group on
OL,15,FSaturday, Roger Harmer said he would
OL,16,Fseek to work with other parties and
OL,17,F"like-minded Independents" to form a
OL,18,Fshared administration for the city.
OL,26,@yD@AOUyD@ZO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/8
