FL,380,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1778523070
OL,3,CLib Dems call for 'like-minded' groups
OL,4,Cto work together post election
OL,6,FThe elections produced a fragmented
OL,7,Fcouncil chamber, with Reform UK
OL,8,Femerging as the largest group on 22
OL,9,Fseats. The Green Party secured 19
OL,10,Fseats, while Labour won 17 and the
OL,11,FConservatives won 16. The Liberal
OL,12,FDemocrats hold 12 seats, alongside 13
OL,13,FIndependents.
OL,15,FTwo seats are still to be declared.
OL,17,FHarmer said the result showed "no one
OL,18,Fparty has the support to be in control
OL,19,Fof the city council" and argued
OL,20,Fcouncillors must now "work together,
OL,21,Ffor the people of Birmingham".
OL,26,@yD@_OU{D@TO]|D@VOU}D@]O]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/8
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,380,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1778523070
OL,3,CLib Dems call for 'like-minded' groups
OL,4,Cto work together post election
OL,6,F"Our proposal is to set out a vision
OL,7,Ffor the city and a supporting delivery
OL,8,Fplan," he said.
OL,10,F"For the past few years, we have been
OL,11,Fknown for financial problems and a
OL,12,Ffailure to collect the bins, but that
OL,13,Fshould not define our city.
OL,15,F"We need to move Birmingham forward as
OL,16,Fa place of initiative, enterprise and
OL,17,Fculture, that attracts people with
OL,18,Ftalent."
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@FO]rD@AOUwD@AOUzD@HO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/8
