PN,37904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1778523070
OL,3,CLib Dems call for 'like-minded' groups
OL,4,Cto work together post election
OL,6,FThe Liberal Democrats said any
OL,7,Fagreement should focus on six
OL,8,Fpriorities, including stabilising the
OL,9,Fcouncil's finances, ending the bin
OL,10,Fdispute, tackling fly-tipping and road
OL,11,Fsafety offences, improving public
OL,12,Fengagement in local decision-making,
OL,13,Fand clearing the backlog of road and
OL,14,Fpavement repairs.
OL,16,FHarmer said the party believed there
OL,17,Fwas "sufficient common ground" between
OL,18,Fpolitical groups to work together and
OL,19,Fcalled for positions of responsibility
OL,20,Fto be shared proportionately.
OL,26,@yD@EOUyD@^O]
